	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "96B2C33445CA9E98E28A2C92DED9EAE1",
		["guid_str"] = "zJCY0KAO",
		["id"] = 4,
		["introduce"] = {
			["location"] = "破晓圣廷·研修院",
			["time"] = "萨格历  18/04/191S.E.",
		},
		["just_auto_play"] = true,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "59252A5E483F5AABC140679BE0B356AE",
		["guid_str"] = "4xx6XT6F",
		["id"] = 5,
		["name"] = "研修院讲师",
		["text"] = "空间魔法即使在高阶魔法中也是较为困难的一种，它的历史可以追溯到……",
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]教室前方的讲师声音平稳地叙述着，一切关于光明与魔法的故事。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "17EC8CB8476CC54F26679ABCC6569A48",
		["guid_str"] = "C64jr4Cw",
		["id"] = 6,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["is_separate_tween"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]透过彩绘玻璃窗投射进纯白的圣廷，染上神圣又迷幻的色彩。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "398D1F9E461F625B5FF1BC90909D3D27",
		["guid_str"] = "fHkJHhin",
		["id"] = 7,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["is_separate_tween"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]而色彩又染上往来进入圣廷的修士，在这里学习法则，拥护法则，\n\n直至纯白的院袍拥有、回归各自的颜色。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "727505A24CDA9D2BBA6B8EB738F33DFB",
		["guid_str"] = "5JRt7UQl",
		["id"] = 8,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["is_separate_tween"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]弗雷德里克低头看着书脊正反着金色光辉的厚重硬质圣书，努力集中精神，\n\n恨不能记下讲师的每句话，又不自觉目光失焦。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "1A1EB71247896C3016F4BD9BBF868A11",
		["guid_str"] = "Fy3wsX40",
		["id"] = 9,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["is_separate_tween"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]有资格入研修院的年轻学徒们会经历不同年限的授课，再接受不同圣廷主祭或高阶骑士的指导与栽培，\n\n最终成为能为圣廷所用、传播秩序和文明之才。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "672494E54E3EDC82646B8FAB550A2D60",
		["guid_str"] = "WINneEx2",
		["id"] = 10,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["is_separate_tween"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]达弗戴尔家族从不缺少尊敬和追捧，毕竟极具象征意义的铂金发色让他们从出生起便拥有了地位，\n\n而自己在家族中只是天赋并不出众，并无什么亮眼之处也不受重视的学徒罢了。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "CC7FB81C48454A6C1AAC6B8DFAA641A2",
		["guid_str"] = "A6FISZMX",
		["id"] = 11,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["is_separate_tween"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]虽然他依旧在学徒间倍受追捧，即便偶尔让他稍觉不安苦恼，不得不说很多时候都让他颇为受用。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "B5FA4A384E789AB60D14BCB9CCF2C5F9",
		["guid_str"] = "bOPAyAcY",
		["id"] = 12,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "B79D4E6E4A59AF4753EF51B014115003",
		["guid_str"] = "X1Sjt90J",
		["id"] = 13,
		["name"] = "弗雷德里克·L·达弗戴尔",
		["text"] = "1，2……5……",
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["align"] = "bottom",
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]原来从5岁被送来研修院，已经是第7年了。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "E4CB21E24290A67313D2A9AAE8B4A198",
		["guid_str"] = "O0i0R04r",
		["id"] = 14,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "73ADA72A4F21E786844156BC3BF66F2B",
		["guid_str"] = "BkIF8tOn",
		["id"] = 15,
		["name"] = "弗雷德里克·L·达弗戴尔",
		["text"] = "怎么还是学徒……唉……",
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "B95A1732462D43F5525D29A1D12AD147",
		["guid_str"] = "Ho3FlvwU",
		["id"] = 16,
		["name"] = "弗雷德里克·L·达弗戴尔",
		["text"] = "不过……",
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]弗雷德里克合上书，看向厚重书面上的几枚烫金符号。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "35F1D15940BE321CC6282392A07B50C7",
		["guid_str"] = "hn2M4UZt",
		["id"] = 17,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]从研修院获得身份，尤其在得到几位主祭或是圣廷骑士团的肯定后，\n\n会有亲自见到「圣冕」的机会。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
		},
		["guid"] = "F8D41EA1444D07F1B25821A3A905EE01",
		["guid_str"] = "t33YxBda",
		["id"] = 18,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]——直到去年为止。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
		},
		["guid"] = "FFC5CFF7400DCE82BF882E9732B9A3F6",
		["guid_str"] = "AbX0qdrF",
		["id"] = 19,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "64AAC6BF46FFF38C55EB269180AA7279",
		["guid_str"] = "pQPvmJno",
		["id"] = 20,
		["name"] = "弗雷德里克·L·达弗戴尔",
		["text"] = "……呼……虽然不知道为什么，但还好终止了……",
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]所有直面「圣冕」之人，首先感受到的，都是令人无法抬头也无法拒绝的威严。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "104E6C134882D59E9F4011AC60770125",
		["guid_str"] = "tT8iCYPU",
		["id"] = 21,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]是金色。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
		},
		["guid"] = "CFFD7DDF4E1BD5A6205E7E8528A29E41",
		["guid_str"] = "bwZoKftx",
		["id"] = 22,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]这是从前光明主祭轻拍他的头告诉他的。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
		},
		["guid"] = "11CE93A849F121C34549D3BFD75CA724",
		["guid_str"] = "IOTFZTqg",
		["id"] = 23,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]说实话，他并没有勇气面对那种压倒性的威严，\n\n即便光明主祭走后再无其他主祭愿意倾心授予他黎威尔的万物知识，\n\n他或许根本不需要这份多余的忧心。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
		},
		["guid"] = "C2FB63604E737356BD707E9BA94F12C0",
		["guid_str"] = "aFvMO5UF",
		["id"] = 24,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]达弗戴尔家族也没那么需要他。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
		},
		["guid"] = "203B12F84133572680342FB67F00934C",
		["guid_str"] = "MYAW0NUF",
		["id"] = 25,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "0CF6A20B4EB88F1EEA347D8EF9ADE7DD",
		["guid_str"] = "X5aC6CFg",
		["id"] = 26,
		["name"] = "弗雷德里克·L·达弗戴尔",
		["text"] = "唉……",
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]又一声没忍住的有些突兀的叹气，弗雷德里克感觉到身边有什么东西动了动，\n\n忽然回神自己还在课堂上，不等他重新让笔尖动起来——",
			["text_align"] = "center",
			["tween"] = {
				{
					["param"] = {
						["delay"] = 0,
						["time"] = 500,
					},
					["tween"] = "FadeIn",
				},
			},
		},
		["guid"] = "0B3C78AF47E120AF0021DAA2C6804AED",
		["guid_str"] = "Xmuh7xTY",
		["id"] = 27,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/DialogRCSceneBG/bg_tourmaline_06.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["characters"] = {
			{
				["anim"] = "normal",
				["blur"] = {
					["material"] = "M_UI_SpineBlur",
				},
				["color"] = {
					0.0,
					0.0,
					0.0,
					0.62745100259781,
				},
				["material"] = "M_UI_SpineMat",
				["path"] = "n50tmlenormal_m/n50tmlenormal_m_action1",
				["shadow"] = {
					["material"] = "M_UI_SpineShadow",
				},
				["tween"] = {
					{
						["param"] = {
							["delay"] = 0,
							["direction"] = "left",
							["dis"] = 100,
							["end_alpha"] = 1.0,
